description:
&lt;p&gt;We are currently recruiting for Registered Nurses to come and join our team to provide Critical Care services. All staff will rotate through the Critical Care Unit as well as HDU and therefore successful candidates will become competent in caring for level 2 and level 3 patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;New starters will receive a comprehensive induction and will be supported to complete the National STEPs Critical Care Competencies; we also run regular study days in the hospital high fidelity simulation suite.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Southend-On-Sea is an exciting place to live, work and enjoy life. Just under an hour from London and Europe can be easily reached through our local airport. The surrounding area is vibrant and cosmopolitan. Local schools have an excellent reputation and the nearby seaside provides a pleasant backdrop as well as opportunities for fun or relaxation. The attractive nearby town of Leigh-On-Sea provides an alternative location for many professionals to settle and wind down after work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a friendly and supportive team who are passionate about doing a good job and providing quality care for the community we serve, both today and in the future.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
